              ④.post来一次完整的：
                  ⑴.request("https://xxx.com/url=https://xxx.com",{headers:{"content-type": "application/json","Referer":"https://xxxx.com","Cookie":"hdhdhdhd"},body:JSON.stringify({"id":"haha"}),method:"POST"});
                  ⑵.要注意body与method前都有逗号
